{"tid":2003824,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla市值週二達標  Elon Musk可獲7.06億美元股權獎勵","createTime":"2020-05-06T05:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:46:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7a62c7e228a90717abc69e6130d110435fcf1fc3","tid":2003824,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕特斯拉（Tesla）股價市值在週二達到了半年平均1000億美元的門檻，這代表馬斯克（Elon Musk）符合獲取7.06億美元（約新台幣210.65億）股票期權獎勵的資格。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》彙編的數據，特斯拉過去半年平均市值在週二收盤已達到1000億美元以上，按照馬斯克的薪酬計畫，滿足這項市值條件，馬斯克可動用12批股票期權獎勵的第1批。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克獲得的首批選擇權可採每股350.02美元的價格，購買特斯拉169萬份股。由於特斯拉股價週二上升0.9%至768.21美元，代表這項期權獎勵價值達7.06億美元，若馬斯克將其全部套現，即可獲得這筆金額。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，馬斯克與董事會達成的完整薪酬方案，包括2030萬份期權，共分為12個批次，若馬斯克實現所有目標，估計可獲得逾500億美元的收益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3156288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3156288&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=badc6f95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3156288&h=3ae78b5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3156288</a>"},{"pid":"6afa491dfd7d831cbc201bebcde90ccb36a778db","tid":2003824,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"幾時捐錢？"},{"pid":"cdbd454735797e516e348829b0d6af88a98cecbc","tid":2003824,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"對佢黎講可能只係普通人出雙糧, 不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6feb4f7359e0ed48136334dddd6e0e14c17cb1","tid":2003824,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6afa491dfd7d831cbc201bebcde90ccb36a778db","tid":2003824,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"幾時捐錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"武